f=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/magic/spells/c/choco-esuna\">Choco Esuna</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/magic/spells/c/choco-life\">Choco Life</a>, or&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/magic/spells/c/choco-recharge\">Choco Recharge</a>. (1/day), chosen when the chocobo knight gains 12th level. If ability picked is the same at the 12th level, it instead increases the number of usages by 1.</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 9.71194%;\">17th</td>\n<td style=\"width: 89.7407%;\">&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 9.71194%;\">18th</td>\n<td style=\"width: 89.7407%;\">&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 9.71194%;\">19th</td>\n<td style=\"width: 89.7407%;\">&nbsp;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td style=\"width: 9.71194%;\">20th</td>\n<td style=\"width: 89.7407%;\">Ability Scores&nbsp;Str +2, Dex +2, Con +2, Wis +2.&nbsp;Special&nbsp;Attacks:&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/magic/spells/c/choco-halo\">Choco Halo</a>,&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/magic/spells/c/choco-trishot\">Choco Trishot</a>, or&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/magic/spells/c/choco-omnishot\">Choco Omnishot</a>. (1/day), chosen when the chocobo knight gains 20th level.</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"changes":[],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"links":{"children":[],"classAssociations":[{"id":"ffd20-content.ffd20-class-mounts.iBVUphdKa36xmHAE","dataType":"compendium","name":"Chocobo Bite","img":"systems/ffd20/icons/FFxiv%20icons/FFXIVIcons%20MainCommand%20(Others)/01_Orders/01/free_stance.png","hiddenLinks":{},"level":1,"_index":0},{"id":"ffd20-content.ffd20-class-mounts.BpF78uRKogSAvGWM","dataType":"compendium","name":"Chocobo Claw","img":"systems/ffd20/icons/FFxiv%20icons/FFXIVIcons%20MainCommand%20(Others)/01_Orders/01/free_stance.png","hiddenLinks":{},"level":1,"_index":1},{"id":"ffd