Texture":""},"attackName":"","actionType":"mwak","attackBonus":"","critConfirmBonus":"","damage":{"parts":[["1d6","S"]],"critParts":[],"nonCritParts":[]},"attackParts":[],"formulaicAttacks":{"count":{"formula":"","value":null},"bonus":{"formula":""},"label":""},"formula":"","ability":{"attack":"str","damage":"str","damageMult":1,"critRange":20,"critMult":2},"save":{"dc":"0","type":"","description":""},"effectNotes":"","attackNotes":"","soundEffect":"","links":{"children":[],"charges":[]},"tag":"chocoboClaw","useCustomTag":false,"flags":{"boolean":[],"dictionary":[]},"attackType":"natural","masterwork":false,"nonlethal":false,"enh":null,"proficient":true,"primaryAttack":true,"showInQuickbar":true,"broken":false,"held":"normal","conditionals":[],"attack":{"parts":[]}},"sort":700000,"flags":{"ffd20":{}},"img":"systems/ffd20/icons/FFxiv%20icons/FFXIVIcons%20MainCommand%20(Others)/01_Orders/01/free_stance.png","effects":[]},{"_id":"uW0jNbVmWRy229Ab","name":"Mount - Class Abilities","type":"class","data":{"description":{"value":"<p>This should be the level of the Chocobo Knight</p>\n<p>A chocobo knight gains the service of a loyal and trusty yellow chocobo to carry him into battle. This chocobo functions as a beastmaster&rsquo;s animal companion, using the chocobo knight&rsquo;s level as his effective beastmaster level. A chocobo knight&rsquo;s mount does not gain the shared saves special ability. If a chocobo knight enhances his chocobo mount with&nbsp;<a href=\"https://www.finalfantasyd20.com/equipment/chocobo-food/\">chocobo food</a>, all permanent food buffs carry over in advancements. But if the chocobo knight&rsquo;s chocobo mount dies, all permanent food buffs are lost if he summons a new one.<br />Unlike normal chocobos of its kind, a chocobo&rsquo;s Hit Dice, abilities, skills, and feats advance as the chocobo knight advances in level. If a character receives a companion from more than one source, his effective chocobo knight levels stack for the purposes of determining the statistics and abilities of the companion.</p>\n<h2 id=\"tablepress-440-name\">Table: Chocobo Mount Base Statistics</h2>\n<table id=\"tablepress-440\" aria-labelledby=\"tablepress-440-name\">\n<thead>\n<tr>\n<th>Class Level</th>\n<th>Natural Armor Bonus</th>\n<th>Str/Dex Bonus</th>\n<th>Bonus Tricks</th>\n<th>Special</th>\n</tr>\n</thead>\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td>1st</td>\n<td>+0</td>\n<td>+0</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>Link, Endurance</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>2nd</td>\n<td>+0</td>\n<td>+0</td>\n<td>1</td>\n<td>&mdash;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>3rd</td>\n<td>+2</td>\n<td>+1</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>Evasion</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>4th</td>\n<td>+2</td>\n<td>+1</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>&mdash;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>5th</td>\n<td>+2</td>\n<td>+1</td>\n<td>2</td>\n<td>Ability score increase</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>6th</td>\n<td>+4</td>\n<td>+2</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>Devotion</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>7th</td>\n<td>+4</td>\n<td>+2</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>&mdash;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>8th</td>\n<td>+4</td>\n<td>+2</td>\n<td>3</td>\n<td>Multiattack</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>9th</td>\n<td>+6</td>\n<td>+3</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>&mdash;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>10th</td>\n<td>+6</td>\n<td>+3</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>Ability score increase</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>11th</td>\n<td>+6</td>\n<td>+3</td>\n<td>4</td>\n<td>&mdash;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>12th</td>\n<td>+8</td>\n<td>+4</td>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>&mdash;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>13th</td>\n<td>+8</td>\n<td>+4</td>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>&mdash;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>14th</td>\n<td>+8</td>\n<td>+4</td>\n<td>5</td>\n<td>&mdash;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>15th</td>\n<td>+10</td>\n<td>+5</td>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>Ability score increase, Improved Evasion</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>16th</td>\n<td>+10</td>\n<td>+5</td>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>&mdash;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>17th</td>\n<td>+10</td>\n<td>+5</td>\n<td>6</td>\n<td>&mdash;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>18th</td>\n<td>+12</td>\n<td>+6</td>\n<td>7</td>\n<td>Blood Bond</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>19th</td>\n<td>+12</td>\n<td>+6</td>\n<td>7</td>\n<td>&mdash;</td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>20th</td>\n<td>+12</td>\n<td>+6</td>\n<td>+7</td>\n<td>&mdash;</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<p><br />A chocobo knight does not take an armor check penalty on Ride checks while riding his mount. The mount is always considered combat trained, and begins play with Endurance as a bonus feat. A chocobo knight&rsquo;s bond with his mount is strong, with the pair learning to anticipate each other&rsquo;s moods and moves. Should a chocobo knight&rsquo;s mount die, the chocobo knight may find another chocobo to serve him after 1 week of mourning. This new mount does not gain the link, evasion, devotion, improved evasion, or blood bond special abilities until the next time the chocobo knight gains a level.</p>\n<p>Class Level:&nbsp;The character&rsquo;s chocobo knight level. The chocobo knight&rsquo;s class levels stack with levels of any other classes that are entitled to a companion for the purpose of determining the companion&rsquo;s statistics.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Natural Armor Bonus:&nbsp;The number noted here is an improvement to the chocobo&rsquo;s existing natural armor bonus.</li>\n<li>Str/Dex Bonus:&nbsp;Add this value to the chocobo&rsquo;s Strength and Dexterity scores.</li>\n<li>Bonus Tricks:&nbsp;The value given in this column is the total number of &ldquo;bonus&rdquo; tricks that the animal knows in addition to any that the chocobo knight might choose to teach it (see the Handle Animal skill). These bonus tricks don&rsquo;t require any training time or Handle Animal checks, and they don&rsquo;t count against the normal limit of tricks known by the chocobo. The chocobo knight selects these bonus tricks, and once selected, they can&rsquo;t be changed.</li>\n<li>Link (Ex):&nbsp;A chocobo knight can handle his companion as a free action, or push it as a move action, even if he doesn&rsquo;t have any ranks in the Handle Animal skill. The chocobo knight gains a +4 competence bonus on all Handle Animal checks made regarding his chocobo.</li>\n<li>Evasion (Ex):&nbsp;If the chocobo is subjected to an attack that normally allows a Reflex saving throw for half damage, it takes no damage if it makes a successful saving throw.</li>\n<li>Devotion (Ex):&nbsp;The chocobo gains a +4 morale bonus on Will saves against enfeebling spells and effects.</li>\n<li>Ability Score Increase (Ex):&nbsp;The chocobo adds +1 to any one of its ability scores.</li>\n<li>Multiattack:&nbsp;The chocobo gains Multiattack as a bonus feat even though it does not have three or more natural attacks. The chocobo instead gains a second attack with its primary natural weapon, albeit at a &ndash;5 penalty.</li>\n<li>Improved Evasion (Ex):&nbsp;When subjected to an attack that normally allows a Reflex saving throw for half damage, the chocobo takes no damage if it makes a successful saving throw and half damage if the saving throw fails.</li>\n<li>Blood Bond (Ex): After a chocobo knight has achieved 18th level, the bond between him and his chocobo grows so strong that the chocobo gains a +2 bonus on all attack rolls, checks and saves if it witnesses the chocobo knight being threatened or harmed. This bonus lasts as long as the threat is immediate and apparent.</li>\n</ul>","chat":"","unidentified":""},"tags":[],"changes":[{"_id":"wfdjsdp6","formula":"floor(@classes.mountClassAbilities.lvl/3)*2","operator":"add","target":"ac","subTarget":"nac","modifier":"untyped","priority":0,"value":0},{"_id":"zo8oaibq","formula":"floor(@classes.mountClassAbilities.lvl/3)","operator":"add","target":"ability","subTarget":"str","modifier":"untyped","priority":0,"value":0},{"_id":"o6epwu3d","formula":"floor(@classes.mountClassAbilities.lvl/3)","operator":"add","target":"ability","subTarget":"dex","modifier":"untyped","priority":0,"value":0}],"changeFlags":{"loseDexToAC":false,"noEncumbrance":false,"mediumArmorFullSpeed":false,"heavyArmorFullSpeed":false},"links":{"children":[],"classAssociations":[{"id":"ffd20.feats.ehqx8txNRGMaNOPt","dataType"